            simple (and delicious) to keep your family on track!
          </p>
        </div>
        <img
          src="{{ 'plane.png' | asset_url }}"
          alt="Plane"
          class="w-full h-auto lg:pt-10 transform md:max-w-[300px] md:mx-auto lg:w-[80%] lg:-translate-x-[15%] lg:mx-0"
